<p><span class="anchor" id="p48"></span>أَي الاقارب<a href="#p48" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p49"></span>فَقَط اعْتبر<a href="#p49" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p50"></span>ذَلِك فى الْمَطْلُوب مهرهَا بِالنِّسْبَةِ لمن ذكر<a href="#p50" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p51"></span>وَيجب<a href="#p51" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p52"></span>فى وَطْء نِكَاح فَاسد مهر مثل يَوْم الْوَطْء فان تكَرر<a href="#p52" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p53"></span>الْوَطْء<a href="#p53" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
